{"tid":546122,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]火影忍者 疾風亂舞 (110)四代活動進行中 大家記得肝啦","createTime":"2018-01-31T08:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T20:14:20.000Z","uid":40640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c38ddc83f2c3729e14c78346405bffa5f4f81f83","tid":546122,"uid":40640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"[quote]<strong>官網</strong> (附ios/an下載點) <br />\n<a href=\"http://narucole.jp/?at=1l3vkMx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnarucole.jp%2F%3Fat%3D1l3vkMx&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d360aa69\" target=\"_blank\">http://narucole.jp/?at=1l3vkMx</a> <br />\n<strong>官方email address</strong><br />\nnarucole@help.gree.net <br />\n<br />\n<strong>官方宣傳GAMEPLAY</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M4fkx4Fu1uM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM4fkx4Fu1uM&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=d8b03754\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M4fkx4Fu1uM</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>攻略Wiki</strong> (日文,唔update): <br />\n<a href=\"http://naruto.upwiki.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnaruto.upwiki.net%2F&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ac281b2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://naruto.upwiki.net/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>本post吉祥物</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WA94W0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WA94W0.jpg&h=1d99f3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9k4RbFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9k4RbFA.jpg&h=13546ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>人人一抽入魂中新限</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>高登好友list </strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uAP04wns2J2RzrySxJkggFqKv4B13npf2R1UDp6Z7tE/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1uAP04wns2J2RzrySxJkggFqKv4B13npf2R1UDp6Z7tE%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2a64fd1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uAP04wns2J2RzrySxJkggFqKv4B13npf2R1UDp6Z7tE/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*新手請睇曬post頭先發問*</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nPost頭目錄<br />\n1.刷首抽教學<br />\n2.首抽建議(部分)<br />\n3.常見日文&amp;辭彙解釋<br />\n4.常見FAQ (紅字一定要睇)<br />\n5.疾風傳(主線任/物語任)拎石條件<br />\n6.無所屬隊介紹&amp;心得<br />\n7.曉隊介紹&amp;心得<br />\n8.PVP心得<br />\n<br />\n給新手的話:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n雖然入到黎見老玩家三句唔埋就屌營運點閪點撚狗, 但呢隻GAME 本身絕對係一個好遊戲, 無論畫風, 操作方法, 平衡性(目前為止)黎講可玩性都算唔錯。GAME名 &quot;collections&quot; says it all, 課金有課金玩法, 無課有無課玩法, 當佢儲卡GAME就好, 罕有角難出係定律黎, N抽唔到限止蝕好緊要, 因為金錢有限, 但限角就會不斷出, 今次追唔到總有一次會出你有愛既角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> That's the meaning of collections<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滿11忍揀技速 記住 記住 記住</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">新手頭一星期無限體，曜日任務有錢／覺醒料／肥料</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>課金注意事項 </strong><br />\n用日本itunes下載遊戲再轉地區做香港課金, 會出現遊戲更新唔到嘅情況, 所以最好都係買日本itunes卡<br />\n<br />\n<strong>刷首抽教學 </strong><br />\n<em>*由於模擬器已被ban，以往電腦快刷方法已失效，若仍欲知詳情請自行搜尋(73)或之前嘅post*</em><br />\n首先準備兩部電話or devices<br />\n電話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>係拎黎刷首抽，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">B</span></strong>係拎黎洗走<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>抽完嘅ac<br />\n操作步驟如下：<br />\n<strong>1. </strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">B</span></strong>停喺開波未入game個標題畫面 (即係輸入引繼嗰度)<br />\n<strong>2. </strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>正常入game開ac，skip教學 (打完名一句野都未彈出黎前瘋狂撳抽卡粒掣就skip到)，抽完一次<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">假首抽</span></strong>會更新，更新完就可以拎禮物箱嘅石，開始<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">真首抽</span></strong>，抽完唔啱心水就去右下角settings，撳第二粒掣發行引繼碼<br />\n<strong>3. </strong>拎起<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">B</span></strong>，輸入完引繼碼就會load，跟住繼續停係未入game個標題畫面<br />\n<strong>4. </strong>拎起<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></strong>是旦撳個掣，會彈出error信息話俾你聽ac已經被引繼走，撳完ok後會返回標題畫面，至此為一次首抽流程<br />\n<strong>5. </strong>重複步驟1-4，因為早前已經更新過，第二次打後嘅首抽流程就唔使更新，一分鐘內就能夠完成一次<br />\n<br />\n<strong>巴打製角色評價</strong>(outdated<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qsLMB9lRO4EKuZ3GTwAFq4oG6J8Mtp5mTmgX-rQUa7c/pub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1qsLMB9lRO4EKuZ3GTwAFq4oG6J8Mtp5mTmgX-rQUa7c%2Fpub&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bd0c39e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qsLMB9lRO4EKuZ3GTwAFq4oG6J8Mtp5mTmgX-rQUa7c/pub</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>巴打新製角色評價(持續更新)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XpwrsjgyAy2D__uXclKX5HD2qJQWiT55Ib9LThSA5ug/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1XpwrsjgyAy2D__uXclKX5HD2qJQWiT55Ib9LThSA5ug%2Fedit&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=07e8ec60\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XpwrsjgyAy2D__uXclKX5HD2qJQWiT55Ib9LThSA5ug/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>首抽建議</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/KwIraO7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKwIraO7.png&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=874b1f09\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/KwIraO7.png</a>此４角已變時代眼淚，但仍有一定地位, 首抽計搏下面幾隻為佳"},{"pid":"ea4c8