25d5c0dfba5285b11fbce248bce74.png&h=2773f0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單抽燒卡出屍鬼四代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"單抽撚全面進埸"},{"pid":"018b88ec5495db18f3ca69fbee2f145bef8b6a2b","tid":546122,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"輕鬆31.5 倍 唔抽了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ccccea1a6baa3b46a56a71bbb8557308db1ca4","tid":546122,"uid":40640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"征龍巴，都係你開啦，2500字依個問題唔知點搞"},{"pid":"90de431af56e91d56b126e7e5d6dc3165ffe6c93","tid":546122,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d68c2f5d45f7402842a1707ebd6554404335ce48","tid":546122,"uid":82676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/162133_9210f7924ea8599048ff110f43a73b34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F162133_9210f7924ea8599048ff110f43a73b34.png&h=8373ae49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想要阿媽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw呢隻好唔好用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1c854e98a1f9050c5d36e905f8d19e4c364bc9","tid":546122,"uid":40640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>首抽建議</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/KwIraO7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKwIraO7.png&d=gTyQCL0llkviVWn5Pni7IozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=874b1f09\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/KwIraO7.png</a>此４角已變時代眼淚，但仍有一定地位, 首抽計搏下面幾隻為佳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AIu98dT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAIu98dT.png&h=4c1ea9d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/120914_c4f610f66f91c47a21d9f5855a039a90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F120914_c4f610f66f91c47a21d9f5855a039a90.jpg&h=26d18140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>常見日文辭彙</strong><br />\nキャラクター/ <br />\nキャラ\t----------- 角色 <br />\nチャクラ ----------- 查克拉/卓羅 <br />\nアップ\t----------- Up <br />\nダウン\t----------- Down <br />\nスキル\t----------- 技能 <br />\nタイプ\t----------- 遁 <br />\nダメージ ----------- 傷害 <br />\nスキルダメージ ----------- 技能傷害 <br />\nキャンセル\t----------- 取消 <br />\nランキングイベント ----------- Ranking Event <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>常見辭彙</strong><br />\n<strong>超忍祭/超超忍祭</strong> ----------- 即係限定up，超超忍會有新限定追加<br />\n<strong>祭札</strong> ----------- 每逢超忍抽十連會有一札，夠20札可以去商店換限定券，30札可以自選一隻限<br />\n<strong>P幣</strong> ----------- 只要用1石就會有2個P幣，有時會有多幾倍up，去商店有得換每個月更新嘅角色同其他道具<br />\n<strong>專武</strong> ----------- 角色專有忍具，當配落特定角色時文字描述會變<span style=\"color: red;\">紅字</span>，觸發特別效果<br />\n<strong>PvP</strong>\t----------- 昇級試驗，間唔中會出嘅1對1 event<br />\n<strong>共鬥任務</strong> ----------- lv 1 至 lv 50嘅挑戰任務<br />\n<strong>忍道</strong> ----------- 相同角色自食會升忍道，每升一下會加三圍基礎數値，滿忍道係11/11，滿忍道後可以自選一個bonus ability，暫時大部分角色都係選擇加技速<br />\n<strong>推薦狀</strong> ----------- 用黎升忍道，5星必升，3/4星確率升<br />\n<strong>信賴度</strong> ----------- 信賴度係以角色計，並唔係以卡計，如果想儘快升一個角色嘅信賴度，可以全隊入同一個角色嘅卡，最後結算信賴度一樣會全部加入同一個角色<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一關入面隊長得到嘅信賴度係隊員兩倍</span>[/quote]"},{"pid":"317be6259aa89b8e107c733362fc7d0a599aecbe","tid":546122,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"50抽食晒屎 中得隻舊鳴媽 放置play<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2cd9a790e34f7212705f61362b3c8370f6f7c2","tid":546122,"uid":135928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"cd1749bf627158130149f51c3dd0dbdd0055cf13","tid":546122,"uid":40640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"[quote]<strong>FAQ </strong><br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 新手抽咩pool開局？<br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 抽開催緊嘅超忍pool，記住唔好抽<span style=\"color: red;\">新手嗰個超忍pool</span>，大伏嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 更新卡住點算? <br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 可以係入game前, 撳右上角引繼隔離個制(ios係引繼下面, 最低果個) ,唔得嘅話就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> load入關卡黑畫面同樣方法 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 唔同機種引繼會唔會冇哂啲石？<br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 唔會 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">新手首抽完有咩做？</span><br />\n<strong>A.</strong><br />\n1.專武 ------ 去event任務撳概要，睇下而家有冇得打首抽角色嘅專武，要留意大部分任務有限時<br />\n2.上6星 ------ 覺醒首抽角色到6星，曜日任務打覺醒素材同強化素材，6星覺醒素材要去打忍玉<br />\n3.儲石 ------ 打主線任務拎石，屬於次要<br />\n4.刷難關 ------ 大部分關最後都需要40/50體，新手體力最大值未夠可以去商店&quot;アイテム一覽&quot;食拉麵回體，會將你現時用淨嘅體力加上最大值，假設最大值係30體，用到剩20體時再食拉麵就會有20+30=50體<br />\n5.出門靠朋友 ------ 呢個唔使解釋啦掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新手首抽完有咩要留意?</span></strong><br />\n1. 入關前可以禁＂？＂(概要)，睇下打呢關有咩獎勵/用咩角會有特效(point+傷害)。<br />\n2.  <strong>&quot;報酬詳細&quot;</strong> : 每關都可以係揀任果到詳細睇有乜送。<span style=\"color: red;\">補充：有時Ｓ評級／打多幾次獎勵會更多。</span><br />\n3. <strong>&quot;攻略情報&quot;</strong> : 關於boss嘅弱點/無效技能、行動(例如幾時會用大技)、弱體同異常狀態有冇效等。<span style=\"color: red;\">補充：好重要，如果ｂｏｓｓ雷遁無效，你用招雷遁技本身傷害幾高都扣唔到佢血。</span><br />\n4. <strong>商店-交換所</strong> : 可以交換素材, 換友情point, 買製造忍具嘅書(買1次永久用, 但部份忍具書要打任先送) <span style=\"color: red;\">補充：每個月都可以用忍幣換石，最多25粒記得換! 忍幣可以靠賣野強化醒覺打關拎到。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> 傷害點計？ <br />\n<strong>A.</strong> <br />\nType1: 攻擊力% xxx - 攻擊力越高，傷害越大，唔睇對手三圍 <br />\nType2: 倍數傷害 - 攻擊力越高，對手防禦越低，傷害越大。所以減防有用 <br />\nType3: 最大HP% - 扣對手最大HP既xx%，不受自身攻擊、對手防禦影響 <br />\nType4: xxxx點固定傷害 - 完全不受雙方三圍影響 <br />\n注意：加技傷(スキルダメージ)既忍具，可以加以上所有種類技能既傷害<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q.</strong> Buff會唔會疊加？ <br />\n<strong>A.</strong> 普通buff係計最新果個 e.g. buff攻防40% 再buff攻速30% 結果 = 攻30%防40%速30% <br />\n特殊狀態本身增幅會疊加，而且可以同其他特殊狀態疊加<br />\n例如：奮30% + 開100% + 普通buff30% = 160%<br />\n如果你之後再普通buff 80%，因為呢個係普通buff, 咁就會取代之前果普通buff30% 變成總共 210%<br />\n注意：一般技傷buff係會比遁buff cover, 例如柱間自buff 120%攻+120%技傷, 如果你再上6星舊鳴個buff (80%速+80%風遁），柱間個120%技傷會消失<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. 唔見左ac點算？<br />\nA. <br />\n<br />\nnarucole@help.gree.net （send 去呢到）<br />\n<br />\nゲームのアカウントを復活させたいですけどなかの忍石が __石（仲有幾多石）<br />\nユーザーIDおよびユーザー名：(ID and game名）<br />\n復旧したいデータご利用時に、使用されていた端末情報：(咩手機同咩型號 e.g. iPhone 6 plus)<br />\n最終ログイン日：（最後幾時on）<br />\nゲームを開始された日：（邊日開始玩）<br />\n忍ランク：（衣家幾多level)<br />\n以前に引継ぎコードを発行している場合は、発行したコードとID情報 （之前既引繼碼）<br />\nご登録いただいている場合は事前登録したメールアドレスと特典のコード （有無事前登録？ 沒就打いいえ）<br />\n忍一覧の所持上限数(忍蔵は含みません)：自已忍box total有幾多上限）<br />\n課金された場合はその情報のスクリーンショット（必ず以下のメールが各ストアから送信されます）(有無課金？ 有就cap返張收據 課金會send收據去返你課金個apple email)<br />\n班で編成していた忍の構成内容：(班用緊咩人物）<br />\n所持しているすべての最高レアリティの「忍」名とそれぞれの所持枚数(レアガチャから獲得できものに限る) （有咩限定卡同有幾多張）<br />\neg うちはサスケ［決別の祈り］x1<br />\n波風ミナト［鎮魂の光耀］x1<br />\n直近の「忍石」の所持数 （最後仲有幾多石）<br />\n初めの「レアガチャ」で獲得した「忍」名 （首抽係咩人物 啫係教學完抽果張垃圾卡）<br />\n最後にクリアした「任務」名 （最後完成係咩任務）<br />\n最後に「覚醒」した「忍」名（最後覺醒既卡係邊張）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新手如有其他疑問歡迎發問，一眾巴打會為你解答</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRanking孖寶：<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l0Iy1lqwGfxN4AKDm/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0Iy1lqwGfxN4AKDm%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f896cb3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7bukeNcvpLDsCtQ4/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o7bukeNcvpLDsCtQ4%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b2f64e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警世通言 <br />\n咁多位巴打請記住每個月都要發行引繼code，仲要cap低或save幅圖喺其他device到，萬一有咩事都仲有得救</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793a947c3a71972a04d0f881e0e081556378df27","tid":546122,"uid":40640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>疾風傳拎石條件　<br />\n<br />\n第一章<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170320_add0a1f98055f80a02dc7c7c916d3b9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170320_add0a1f98055f80a02dc7c7c916d3b9a.jpg&h=b7b990d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小櫻入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170321_534bded129ccb4172a137f7de9975c5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170321_534bded129ccb4172a137f7de9975c5c.jpg&h=f128f8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗚門+小櫻入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170321_ba6450900c9f126d342ce03b0d17f0cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170321_ba6450900c9f126d342ce03b0d17f0cd.jpg&h=7f5d0ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗚門入隊<br />\n<br />\n第二章<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170349_915ddf114b5fb3bf6d13d8722a5c02f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170349_915ddf114b5fb3bf6d13d8722a5c02f7.jpg&h=6e29f67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我愛羅入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170349_354c0c7934508a04b3a231570e211fb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170349_354c0c7934508a04b3a231570e211fb7.jpg&h=d633aab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用過武器技能<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/023611_1ab9fa5a0c855771ab46409dc14d4e55.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F023611_1ab9fa5a0c855771ab46409dc14d4e55.PNG&h=55b3c137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡卡西入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170500_0649414faab6bb8868325ede91fe9155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170500_0649414faab6bb8868325ede91fe9155.jpg&h=e8db1646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凱入隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/170501_f81eca0312b13054ea1186d777daff83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F170501_f81eca0312b13054ea1186d777daff83.jpg&h=1bd13360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鳴門入隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三章 (感謝1min60s(一豬)巴提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161751_b1f09ae855d8f10e06a56830c3e335e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161751_b1f09ae855d8f10e06a56830c3e335e0.jpg&h=a0e4299c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161753_3faa402a7a194acae7f69eb6b46ac27e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161753_3faa402a7a194acae7f69eb6b46ac27e.jpg&h=bd2149ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161754_5ba69c9e2fd2bd4e96eb78fb3b44e503.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161754_5ba69c9e2fd2bd4e96eb78fb3b44e503.jpg&h=c8fa0f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161754_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161754_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg&h=a9e8100f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/161755_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F161755_80ca54b357d3b2c925a2cfd892bd276a.jpg&h=41ff80ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">hard mode 通常夠打就夠條件拎石, 如果都係拎唔到可以comment問巴打</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5feec55a30596621239438391e19df864f447640","tid":546122,"uid":40640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">跟住落黎係巴打嘅心得，包含首抽、組隊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無所屬新手推介＋介紹(濕鳩工程巴提供)</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/053911_4a76456fbcd74a7a3e9b14c05eeba7db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F053911_4a76456fbcd74a7a3e9b14c05eeba7db.jpg&h=b47a1f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新帶土<br />\n新手起手 10／10  實用性10／10<br />\n首先耐性無視可以對應全部關 二來佢唔似舊帶土要全隊無所屬先發揮到op實力<br />\n機本上咩隊都入得<br />\n同埋新手冇忍具 辛苦d滿忍都可以雙閃<br />\n技2扣血 就算無新既排名忍具 用土珠／風土珠可以解決<br />\npvp用黎扑d料理撚又得<br />\n因為泛用性高 所以無所屬黎講佢係最好起手既一隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/051738_1203704de8b4e7a3c7bb195d1fb6b6ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F051738_1203704de8b4e7a3c7bb195d1fb6b6ea.jpg&h=28eb198c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n月讀班<br />\n新手起手 7／10  實用性9／10<br />\n好多新手有個誤解覺得佢打人唔痛 事實佢根本唔係要黎秒人<br />\n佢定位係妨礙角色 同40pain定位唔同<br />\n40pain係半打手半妨礙 月讀班係全妨礙角<br />\n用黎reolad人地條bar／debuff 係打關＆pvp都非常有用<br />\n同時佢組隊都幾彈性 唔需要入無所屬隊就可以發揮實力<br />\n唔好地方係必需旗仔（唔洗滿忍）／求道玉（需滿忍）先達到雙閃效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/053931_042de2e8cf650b80da30053f0e963863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F053931_042de2e8cf650b80da30053f0e963863.jpg&h=1e98bb18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因陀羅<br />\n新手起手 6／10  實用性8／10<br />\n基本上比粒壽紙＋雷珠 <br />\n開下2技就可以閃光 打既傷害極高 而且隊長技實用 容易組隊<br />\n忍具盡量刷粒雷珠就得 因為佢開得因陀羅pool都預左會開埋忍具關比你打<br />\n不過話哂神忍 新手難覺醒<br />\n但總括黎講佢係幾好用既<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/053949_f30d83e20fb56f9cd0eb61b817a196aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F053949_f30d83e20fb56f9cd0eb61b817a196aa.jpg&h=25142ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火循班（知）<br />\n新手起手 4／10 實用性6／10<br />\n高傷 純係一隻唔錯既打手 又可以解人buff 同時唔洗入無所屬隊都得<br />\n忍具必需要旗仔 唔係滿忍都雙閃唔到<br />\n不過用查好多 又裝唔到全獸獸個個減查忍具<br />\n所以冇奶媽就唔太建議上場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下其實唔係新手推介 純介紹比有愛組無所屬既人<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n因為我玩火影開始到而家我基本上都係玩無所屬隊 好老實講句 無所屬條路好長<br />\n首先好食忍具 其次好食忍道 最重要係要齊腳 唔係有愛都唔好組無所屬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/054013_18f1b51f1cd74b9b2eb7868f18e98173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F054013_18f1b51f1cd74b9b2eb7868f18e98173.jpg&h=45495dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生日班<br />\n喱隻班用落真係好勁<br />\n素早好快 係好撚快 傷害比火循班低小小 但裝岩忍具<br />\n佢出二下技＝火循班出一下<br />\n可以將火珠既性能完全發揮<br />\n自已又可以裝到全尾獸／新既結印忍具<br />\n用查量唔算多 我相信打pvp算係一隻好煩膠既角<br />\n唯一唔知算唔算缺點<br />\n佢技2要有柱間先完全發揮到 <br />\n但我自已用落就覺得當佢自加100％素早就算 對面有柱間係bonus<br />\n總體黎講係一隻好撚全面既角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/054029_6939941657d4b586e72ed66a184bf457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F054029_6939941657d4b586e72ed66a184bf457.jpg&h=4c1c0e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n送既帶土<br />\n喱隻又係一隻好撚正既角色<br />\n佢係一隻support＋妨礙既角色<br />\n2技補100查＋無所屬素早200％ <br />\n推佢素早 比部dv機佢開永動機 成隊變小明<br />\n得閒用下1技 博下封印人又得<br />\n好希望未來會出隻強化版既佢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/054042_fd4feb8db3f150dca02c7a064a707402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F054042_fd4feb8db3f150dca02c7a064a707402.jpg&h=29a4efea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊帶土<br />\n唔多講 冇新帶土先用啦 都唔差既</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e0e82f15cb4e3568bf70d63d7f8e2e1e5c0e7264","tid":546122,"uid":38391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:37:53.000Z","msg":"新post LM<br />\n上個post又爭唔到1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f23e37f61b61ae253f0efc8396c4759d669d460","tid":546122,"uid":14536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea4c8bed773ad059e73f810498a908cd776d58b2","tid":546122,"uid":40640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"征龍巴，一開始已經過2千5字，點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我電腦開冇事<br />\n下個PO 我搞搞佢"},{"pid":"1fa99721735ecf05f4377483ca506e89f17b53e7","tid":546122,"uid":16616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b434e090d8fa375d12e189fe875ed4f8d5315854","tid":546122,"uid":38391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31